"""
Hand Gesture Recognition - Single Stream ST-GCN + Mixture of Experts

This script implements a simplified pipeline that:
  1. Loads 3D hand landmark sequences (21 points × 3 coordinates)
  2. Prepares a single graph stream (position + velocity = 6 channels)
  3. Processes through an ST-GCN backbone
  4. Passes features through Mixture-of-Experts layers
  5. Classifies into 13 gesture classes

The architecture is: Landmarks → ST-GCN → MoE → Classifier
Includes optional visualization plots for data exploration, training curves,
and evaluation metrics.
"""

